        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 128. Distribution map of Nannaria minor species group collection localities in the Eastern Piedmont and coast." , "Figure 47. Nannaria cingulata sp. nov. (VMNH, NAN 0041) from Prince Edward Co., Virginia. Red arrow indicates projected prefemoral spine. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." , "Figure 46. Nannaria cingulata sp. nov. coloration A holotype ♂ (VTEC, MPE 02324) orange paranota B non-type ♀ (VTEC, MPE 01881) faint orange stripes. Scale bars: 4.0 mm." , "Figure 45. Nannaria cingulata sp. nov. holotype ♂ (VTEC, MPE 02324) left gonopod A anterior view; red triangle indicates basal lateral bulge; red rectangle indicates cingulum B medial view C posterior view; red arrow indicates small lateral flange on acropodite tip; red oval indicates reduced prefemoral spine. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531231" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531150" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531149" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531148" .

